{\bf Problem\,\,1}
	\sum_{k=1}^\infty \frac{(-1)^n}{n^{\alpha}}\sin{\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}}}e^{\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}}}
 \alpha \in \mathbb {R^+} 
n\to\infty
\frac{1}{n^{\alpha}}\sim\frac{1}{n^{\alpha}}
\sin{\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}}}\sim\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}}
e^{\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}}}\sim 1.
 0 <\alpha \le 1/2. 
{\bf Solution.}
 \sum_{k=1}^\infty \frac{1}{n^{\alpha}}\sin{\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}}}e^{\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}}}\quad \sim \quad\sum_{k=1}^\infty \frac{1}{n^{\alpha+\frac{1}{2}}} 
\alpha+\frac{1}{2}<1 \quad\Rightarrow  \quad \alpha<\frac{1}{2}.
e^{\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}}}
 0 <\alpha \le 1 /2,
\lim_{n\to+\infty}\,\,\frac{1}{n^{\alpha}}\sin{\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}}}e^{\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}}}=0\cdot1=0
a_n=\frac{1}{n^{\alpha}}\sin{\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}}}e^{\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}}}
\frac{1}{n^{\alpha}},\alpha > 0 \quad\text{decreases},
\sin{\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}}} 
\sin{\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}}}\le \frac{1}{\sqrt{n}} \quad \text{and the reciprocal function of the root is decrecente }
e^{\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}}}>e^{\frac{1}{\sqrt{n+1}}}\quad\Rightarrow \quad \frac{1}{\sqrt{n}}>\frac{1}{\sqrt{n+1}}\quad\Rightarrow \quad \sqrt{n+1}>\sqrt{n}
{\bf Problem\,\,2}
	\sum_{k=1}^{+\infty} \,\ (\cos n +2)\left(\frac{(\sqrt{1+\alpha)}}{|1-\alpha|}\right)^n
 \alpha \in \mathbb {R} 
\alpha+\frac12\gt1
\alpha+\frac12\gt0
\sin\frac1{\sqrt{n}}
\sin\frac1{\sqrt{n}}\leqslant\frac1{\sqrt{n}}
\frac1{\sqrt{n}}
1\leqslant 2+\cos n\leqslant3
\beta=\dfrac{\sqrt{1+\alpha}}{|1-\alpha|}
\beta\lt1
